00:33:04,420 --> 00:33:06,070
It was raining until yesterday.

714
00:33:06,070 --> 00:33:09,010
So she gave him rubber boots in case of puddles.

715
00:33:09,570 --> 00:33:11,140
I'm happy.

716
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:13,800
He was looking forward to going on errand.

717
00:33:12,810 --> 00:33:14,300
So he wanted to.

718
00:33:13,960 --> 00:33:16,580
Usually his brothers are asked to do it.

719
00:33:17,070 --> 00:33:19,300
The third in the row who is expected less of.

720
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:22,360
He's called cute and treated like a baby.

721
00:33:22,970 --> 00:33:26,260
Masashi dislikes those times.

722
00:33:27,140 --> 00:33:28,760
Closed?

723
00:33:29,030 --> 00:33:31,400
Today is the first time he is being relied on.

724
00:33:31,810 --> 00:33:33,720
The stakes are high, third son.

725
00:33:33,530 --> 00:33:34,450
Do your best.

726
00:33:36,940 --> 00:33:38,450
Did you come by yourself?

727
00:33:38,450 --> 00:33:40,450
Where's your mother?

728
00:33:39,540 --> 00:33:40,460
Welcome.

729
00:33:41,170 --> 00:33:41,940
Home.

730
00:33:41,940 --> 00:33:43,640
Waiting at home?

731
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:45,450
Aren't you usually with your brothers?

732
00:33:45,610 --> 00:33:46,590
What do you want?

733
00:33:46,590 --> 00:33:48,590
Toro as remuneration, right?

734
00:33:48,860 --> 00:33:52,520
The similar thing as tuna, please.

735
00:33:52,520 --> 00:33:54,790
Tuna and salmon?

736
00:33:54,790 --> 00:33:56,100
Both?

737
00:33:56,420 --> 00:33:59,520
He neither understood remuneration or toro.

738
00:33:59,860 --> 00:34:01,640
Poor thing. It changed.

739
00:34:00,980 --> 00:34:05,800
When the old man heard the word similar he gave him the same thing his mom usually buys.

740
00:34:05,800 --> 00:34:07,100
Will this do?

741
00:34:07,100 --> 00:34:08,630
What about the toro?

742
00:34:08,630 --> 00:34:11,400
The lean tuna meat and salmon. Not exactly renummeration.

743
00:34:11,400 --> 00:34:12,970
That will be 1080 yen.

744
00:34:12,970 --> 00:34:14,270
Ended up being cheaper.

745
00:34:14,760 --> 00:34:17,030
This triumphant face.

746
00:34:18,240 --> 00:34:19,440
What a nice face.

747
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:21,300
It will do even if it isn't toro.

748
00:34:21,300 --> 00:34:22,110
That's right.

749
00:34:22,110 --> 00:34:23,900
The shop owners are observing.

750
00:34:23,900 --> 00:34:25,680
Eaten together isn't it like Toro anyway?

751
00:34:29,440 --> 00:34:30,860
He looks happy.

752
00:34:32,570 --> 00:34:33,860
With great delight.

753
00:34:35,490 --> 00:34:36,960
He picked something up.

754
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:38,610
A single leaf.

755
00:34:42,670 --> 00:34:44,990
And now for the 3 white baskets.

756
00:34:44,990 --> 00:34:46,760
