00:35:19,670 --> 00:35:22,040
The same one.

776
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:22,040
The same one?

777
00:35:22,040 --> 00:35:23,090
Like that one?

778
00:35:23,090 --> 00:35:25,160
Oh no, he shouldn't have brought this.

779
00:35:25,580 --> 00:35:27,260
Pigeon.

